        },
        {
            "title": "日本提前選舉猜測升溫之際 植田和男暗示央行加息路徑不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"日本提前選舉猜測升溫之際 植田和男暗示央行加息路徑不變\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8Nc_jjFphuo7k3qCDO9cDA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/7555ea00-f139-11f0-af7f-70993eef215c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">日本提前選舉猜測升溫之際 植田和男暗示央行加息路徑不變</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%8C%9C%E6%B8%AC%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%A4%8D%E7%94%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%94%B7%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-071453288.html",
